body_html:
For help retraining inception5h you can try asking on StackOverflow, but I imagine mainly it's the same as Inception v3 just with different layer names (found in ClassifierActivity.java).

Regarding the latency, Inception v3 is a larger model so it's expected that it will run more slowly. What sort of numbers are you seeing, and on what devices?
